Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Elizabeth Cheatham.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've really enjoyed reading your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we have everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we go down that side?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we didn't go down that side, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like these people walking in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they walking in front of the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I bulked up just for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My bag is not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my favorite kind of shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was like you didn't shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing a good job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not shaking my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you married?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do those two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are familiar with the work to some great degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are new, just so I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, oh dear, so we cannot skip the basics, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we do to accommodate the audience, the mixed audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is we try to review the basics, at least briefly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who haven't been here before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we go on to something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as I get rewired,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the modern world is really,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it was better a couple centuries ago here, I'll tell you folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived in a cave, you had needles and nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and beetles and nuts, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and live in a cave and walk around half naked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they put you away nowadays, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm dressed Hollywood style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a new jacket, gift to me, stunning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she looks pretty ritzy today, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So along the sandals and robes and nuts and beetles,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and along here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what we try to do is represent spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in an entirely new context for the modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because the historic context of religion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was set in a different culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,different side of the planet, different language,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it was presented in a different context.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And since then, man goes back and tries to recreate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and he has to take it on faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes it on faith, he takes it on hearsay,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he takes it from the scriptures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the scriptures, as you'll see from the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth Versus Falsehood, you can say me you knew me when,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth Versus Falsehood, you know what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to people who tell the truth in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reviewing what's happened to the people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,who tell the truth over history, and I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,geezie, you sure you wanna go today, Susie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And all my old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we discovered a means by which to create
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,an entirely different context to validate spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,designed really for modern man who lives in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intellect and science and reason and logic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and provability and computers, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of what relevance is what happened a couple thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ago in a different culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the original ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it got to do with us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it got to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the credibility of religion has deteriorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that the scriptures themselves calibrated lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes considerably lower, than the original avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who spoke them due to misunderstanding by the followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it wasn't written down for a couple of centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever play that parlor game where you whisper something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See what comes out at the other end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the scribes did a little editing of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when you got this plausible representation of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there were so many different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at the history of the New Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the History Channel always has a representation of it periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there were various translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So then everybody had to get together at the Council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and vote on what was legitimate and what wasn't legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't really the way you arrive at truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really go out in space on those kind of speculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't get you out there in a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to base your life on some truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better to be better than hearsay and misunderstandings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and written down by word of mouth for hundreds of years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and then lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In a cave, and oh God, the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're asking a lot of credibility for a modern man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that places his faith in all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if we create a different context then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of a different context,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,clinical science of truth itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,through consciousness research then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a context that is comprehensible to modern man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by which to go back through history, religious history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and validate and revalidate truth from a completely different context
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in which it's irrelevant whether it was true at that time or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care whether what the Buddha said was true or not then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,650 BC, were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's it to you, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you speak Sanskrit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's historical,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which appeals to certain people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,who are authoritative,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,authoritatively oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But our modern society is not authoritatively oriented at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's anti-authoritative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that stupid sticker on people's bumpers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,question authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this jerk to question authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your authority to question authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What they really mean is authoritarianism,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't know the difference between authority and authoritarianism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, it's a rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,rudimentary kind of attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it pervades all of our society and academia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course, relativism as a philosophic political position,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, has really eroded the fabric and caliber of society,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in which things don't have to be truthful anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have a freedom of speech
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the right to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can lie around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your very great right to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we needed a new context.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With which to define what is truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how can it be discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what out of history proves to be valid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by a modern means of examining truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the calibrated level of truth, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,gives us a way to recontextualize all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because the energy field of consciousness itself is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists outside of time and place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and outside of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not subject to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not subject to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you use that, then, as the yardstick,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the absolute Hegel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the German philosopher of the 18th century,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,one of his principles was the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we sort of rediscovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what is that absolute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinitely power, omniscient, omnipresent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the unique thing about consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is it includes all that exists, now or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-linear, everywhere present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the quality of it that makes it very beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is that, curiously, it records every event
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time, on every level,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,thought, feeling, word, deed, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All that happens, every hair on your head
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is not only counted, but numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbered, now we've got them numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, any truth or any event anywhere in history
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,can be obtained right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because outside the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there is only right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's only right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all exists completely everywhere, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sort of mind-boggling to discover that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we discovered the clinical science of kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And inadvertently,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I witnessed the phenomena and merely comprehended it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not see it as local, but as non-local.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was because of my own spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,early in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw things from the viewpoint of context,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from the allness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just was stunned with what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,had been presented with a stimulus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,like an electrostatic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An electrostatic field does nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It just stands there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you present a stimulus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it reacts to an equal and opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This many electrons on this side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you get that many positrons to equal and opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The field itself does nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It just, but it has a capacitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what we're used to seeing in the old speakers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of decades ago, the electrostatic speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had a new way in which to reinvestigate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the book, Truth Versus Falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which came at 5 o'clock last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cliffhanger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We had threats, you either have the book or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, God, honey, I don't know if it's safe to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So 5 o'clock, they showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the publisher, really, was up against the line
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we got the first copies in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First copies in the world, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we got the first copies in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First copies in the world, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we got the first copies in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we got the first copies in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a select group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an historic event, because within myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a student and a scholar, always have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And looking at it as a student and a scholar, I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,man, oh, this is unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this book is like .
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lived through it, it'd be, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They say to tell the truth quickly, leave town,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:17:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tried to recontextualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to recontextualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to recontextualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How it arose, I tried to create a context so that calibrations that would be outside people's expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if you recontextualize it, they'd say, oh, I see why it came out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see why it came out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, during the research, we were surprised to ourselves many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd say, it scratched my head, and we'd repeat it over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd get the same number, and then that would bring up what I needed to know to recontextualize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, when you complete the whole picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth is only true, then, within a context.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And much of fallacy is because you look at content and ignore the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's okay during war is not okay during peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it makes a difference to mention, oh, we happen to be at war at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that does make a bit of a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can say things when you're in the Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're not in the Army, you can't say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're in the Army, because the context changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your responsibility changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your responsibility changes as a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we were talking about that this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,whether my allegiance was to the approval of my colleagues or to the patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was doing innovative work, holistic work at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, not completely approved by academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, is my allegiance to academia or to the healing of this patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I took an oath to heal my patient to the best of my ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm answerable to God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to have to do what I think is going to help this patient to the best of my ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether my colleagues like it or not is going to be their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything you do is controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, traditional medicine is controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychopharmacology is controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But holistic medicine is also controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture is controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being here is controversial, you know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So controversy then just means that it's upsetting somebody's apple cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So evolution is also revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution is revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Jesus Christ said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, I came to bring the sword of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect domestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't translate that into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to bring you spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That does tend to bring some discussion up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find everybody in the world is agreeing with you, you better look out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if there had been no reaction to the book, I would have felt myself a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been disappointed that there's been hardly any rep about it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the introduction of the new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And how it arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings us to an experiential state now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you realize that there is some kind of a guideline to truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you follow it because God expresses it as divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as infinite love, wholeness, allness, oneness, and also as truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So then truth is one of the aspects or qualities of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And devotion is of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you put together the mind and the heart in devotion to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then you know what your alignment is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the rest is automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you align that way and devote your life to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a servant of God and a servant of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be loving towards all of life to the best of your capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't much more that can be asked in this worldly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, also, we're always discovering something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Always something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly, I was writing about, I'm finishing two other books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending Levels of Consciousness, that's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And Doshanam Duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was a little thing in there about out-of-body experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, you know, the near-death experience is transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you calibrate somebody before, level of consciousness before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then after, it makes a huge jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In my life, it made a huge difference, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't really a near-death, but it was equivalent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teenager, recontextualize what the ultimate truth is like, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the radiance of that love is like, poof, outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In contrast, out-of-body experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's calibrated level is the same after as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wondered about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, I mean, it's really amazing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened to me spontaneously several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was rather amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, here's the you, definitely the me, who can see and hear and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,up here, and there's the body down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty clear that you are not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think, boy, that would be a huge jump in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the body is really boring and totally uninteresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the body there and you have absolutely no, no attraction to it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it survives or not is irrelevant, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really strange out-of-body, and anybody out-of-body has experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the self, the consciousness, then, exists independently of the body, because you're
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the other peculiarity is, how can you hear and see if the ears and the eyeballs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are in the body down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's tests, you know, where you put the ears in the eyeballs, you know, and you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,put objects around the room, and, you know, especially during surgery, people go out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of body, and they saw the fan on the top of the cabinet and come back in, so how do you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,see and hear and be and realize the complete and total oneness of the self, and the body's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think, wow, after an experience like that, especially if it happens more than once,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no advance in consciousness after such an amazing, revealing experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So we checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.27,0:24:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer was, because we didn't discover something new, we knew it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you incarnate, you get amnesia for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you incarnate going to amnesia for the other state, otherwise you wouldn't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to tolerate the state, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It agonizes me all the time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go from here to there, and I've got to truck this body with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think, good God, what a nuisance, you know, I'm supposed to out of body, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and there I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just think I'm there, and I'm there instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to drag this thing along with you, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Subject to arthritis and busted bones and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.55,0:24:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So isn't that an interesting discovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So we make those kind of discoveries all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.24,0:24:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it, you knew it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's not a, you know, this is your familiar condition, and this is an arbitrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.38,0:24:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,temporary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:24:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:25:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore it's not a surprise to you, isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We run across things like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.32,0:25:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.23,0:25:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, we were back here talking about the calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.54,0:25:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was therefore a new way to approach religious spiritual reality, reconfirm it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,reexamine it, to see what is the level of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.40,0:25:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the calibrated scale is not better than, but different way, different levels of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.27,0:25:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can express things on the intellectual level, the emotional level, et cetera, the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.90,0:25:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,perceptual level, the linear level, the non-linear level.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.53,0:25:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we could go back and reexamine anything and everything everywhere in history, which
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.64,0:25:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is what the book does.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We did like 7,000 calibrations to arrive at all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.07,0:25:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.07,0:25:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.07,0:25:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.07,0:26:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.77,0:26:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the calibrations don't change over the time because they have to do with historical
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.44,0:26:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,events.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.77,0:26:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Others do because of the change of current events.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So some of the things that were written in 2003, they probably changed a little bit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.22,0:26:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But we delayed publication until hysteria died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.53,0:26:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.53,0:26:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have a new means of recalibrating and reverifying truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.99,0:26:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I like about the consciousness research technique is that it's not just about the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It reaffirms itself, re-corroborates itself, because if this is true, then so-and-so must
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.69,0:26:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.82,0:26:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's constantly reconfirmatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.44,0:26:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It creates a context that is overall comprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.27,0:26:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's very pragmatic, very pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.24,0:26:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited, however, to people 200 and over, calibrate 200 and over, meaning that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:26:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous people who ask an integrous question with an integrity question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.75,0:27:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited, however, to people 200 and over, calibrate 200 and over, meaning that integrous
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,people who ask an integrous question with an integrity question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited, however, to people 200 and over, calibrate 200 and over, meaning that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous people who ask an integrous question with an integrous intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.75,0:27:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who are not integrous and have a non-integrous intention and calibrate below
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.03,0:27:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,200 will think kinesiology doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.03,0:27:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what we said, that it won't work if you're below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.03,0:27:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that reaffirms the truth of kinesiology, that people below 200 can't get the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.03,0:27:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.03,0:27:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.29,0:27:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.29,0:27:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just put up the scale of consciousness one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.29,0:27:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.29,0:27:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.29,0:27:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.29,0:27:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.29,0:27:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.29,0:27:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.55,0:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.68,0:27:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.94,0:27:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.74,0:27:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.74,0:27:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.44,0:27:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, devoting yourself to truth and letting go of the barriers ... So today, we're
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.22,0:27:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about letting go of the barriers, letting go of the resistances to the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.46,0:27:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.97,0:27:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As consciousness evolves, then, truth appears differently to each level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.25,0:28:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 500, love is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's nice, but it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.92,0:28:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 500, love becomes predominantly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.44,0:28:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have a whole change of context
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of meaning, value, worth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.66,0:28:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much you want to devote yourself to it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.53,0:28:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's say the approval of your colleagues
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.51,0:28:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,or critics is a nicety
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not about to devote your life to that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.68,0:28:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,or abandon your devotion, your commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.79,0:28:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the welfare of your patient
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.61,0:28:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if your consciousness is on the level of pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then approval of academia is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.20,0:28:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a priority in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.33,0:28:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the patient will just have to stay sick
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,well I had a very severe ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:28:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it developed in medical school
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:29:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the freshman year
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.14,0:29:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in medical school
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean if you don't get an ulcer in medical school
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something wrong with you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not listening
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.07,0:29:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.92,0:29:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.90,0:29:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.26,0:29:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really a very bad ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.80,0:29:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it caused a lot of agony
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.60,0:29:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.47,0:29:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,did everything possible
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.76,0:29:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived on antispasmodics, antacids
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.54,0:29:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,a diet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.41,0:29:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,just the thought of espresso coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.89,0:29:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,would give you a perforation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.41,0:29:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then periodically
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would get it re-X-rayed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would appear in one part of the duodenum
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.38,0:29:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then it would reappear a year later
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in another ulcer, a different one
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.68,0:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,finally there was one
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that caused severe pain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.66,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in my back excruciating
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.96,0:29:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had to call a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.14,0:29:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a shot of morphine
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.16,0:29:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it was unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.22,0:29:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it was perforating into the pancreas
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.14,0:29:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so the doc says
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.86,0:29:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to get pancreatitis
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the pain is pretty awful
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.00,0:29:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and when he releases narcotics
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.54,0:29:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the pancreatitis patients
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.80,0:30:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,end up addicted to narcotics
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.30,0:30:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave me a grim prognosis
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.65,0:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,well then I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the first acupuncture clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.86,0:30:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.76,0:30:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was established in Washington D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.43,0:30:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it was experimental
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.43,0:30:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you went there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.25,0:30:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an old acupuncturist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.55,0:30:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,from China
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.01,0:30:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and he didn't speak any English
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.40,0:30:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was a translator
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.39,0:30:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but because it was being examined
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.68,0:30:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for its credibility
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.61,0:30:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,any patient accepted there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.85,0:30:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,had to go through
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.64,0:30:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a diagnostic workup first
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.14,0:30:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then after you had
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.81,0:30:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the acupuncture treatments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.90,0:30:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you had to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and repeat the diagnostic workup
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.33,0:30:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.10,0:30:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I went for it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.65,0:30:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated the upper GI series
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.84,0:30:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and sure enough
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.63,0:30:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.21,0:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,very active ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.98,0:30:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.57,0:30:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I went to this acupuncturist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.29,0:30:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I said he didn't speak English
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.61,0:30:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the translator
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.74,0:31:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard acupuncture was painless
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.33,0:31:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the big lie
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.45,0:31:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.82,0:31:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.44,0:31:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I lay down at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.74,0:31:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and these acupuncture needles
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.31,0:31:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he put it right through here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.77,0:31:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it went right through
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.16,0:31:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.28,0:31:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this point right here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.08,0:31:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I screamed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.08,0:31:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I go God man
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.34,0:31:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hardly stay on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.93,0:31:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and he goes ho ho ho
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.17,0:31:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,bad ulcer huh
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.17,0:31:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,this must be your ulcer point folks
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.25,0:31:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody got one
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.25,0:31:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's right here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.25,0:31:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where he did it
